ent\", :subtitle \"猫の人！ こっちです、猫の人！\"} {:seq 2, :duration 10, :speaker :narrator-m, :prompt \"vertical 9:16 live-action, the two exchanging pass cases over people's shoulders both laughing, train sunrise through windows, warm romcom ending wide shot\", :subtitle \"定期の期限は三ヶ月。連絡先の期限は、無し。\"}]}]"}]